queries.question: List all films rented by 'MARY SMITH'
queries.query: SELECT f.title FROM film f JOIN inventory i ON f.film_id = i.film_id JOIN rental r ON i.inventory_id = r.inventory_id JOIN customer c ON r.customer_id = c.customer_id WHERE c.first_name = 'MARY' AND c.last_name = 'SMITH';

queries.question: Which categories has 'MARY SMITH' rented movies from?
queries.query: SELECT DISTINCT cat.name FROM category cat JOIN film_category fc ON cat.category_id = fc.category_id JOIN film f ON fc.film_id = f.film_id JOIN inventory i ON f.film_id = i.film_id JOIN rental r ON i.inventory_id = r.inventory_id JOIN customer c ON r.customer_id = c.customer_id WHERE c.first_name = 'MARY' AND c.last_name = 'SMITH';

queries.question: List actors who appeared in 'Horror' movies
queries.query: SELECT DISTINCT a.first_name, a.last_name FROM actor a JOIN film_actor fa ON a.actor_id = fa.actor_id JOIN film f ON fa.film_id = f.film_id JOIN film_category fc ON f.film_id = fc.film_id JOIN category c ON fc.category_id = c.category_id WHERE c.name = 'Horror' LIMIT 10;

queries.question: Find the most rented film title by customer with ID 1
queries.query: SELECT f.title, COUNT(*) as rent_count FROM film f JOIN inventory i ON f.film_id = i.film_id JOIN rental r ON i.inventory_id = r.inventory_id WHERE r.customer_id = 1 GROUP BY f.title ORDER BY rent_count DESC LIMIT 1;

queries.question: Count 'Action' and 'Comedy' movies in Store 1
queries.query: SELECT c.name, COUNT(*) as film_count FROM category c JOIN film_category fc ON c.category_id = fc.category_id JOIN film f ON fc.film_id = f.film_id JOIN inventory i ON f.film_id = i.film_id WHERE i.store_id = 1 AND c.name IN ('Action', 'Comedy') GROUP BY c.name;

queries.question: Count customers per country
queries.query: SELECT co.country, COUNT(c.customer_id) as customer_count FROM customer c JOIN address a ON c.address_id = a.address_id JOIN city ci ON a.city_id = ci.city_id JOIN country co ON ci.country_id = co.country_id GROUP BY co.country ORDER BY customer_count DESC LIMIT 10;

queries.question: List languages of films featuring 'PENELOPE GUINESS'
queries.query: SELECT DISTINCT l.name FROM language l JOIN film f ON l.language_id = f.language_id JOIN film_actor fa ON f.film_id = fa.film_id JOIN actor a ON fa.actor_id = a.actor_id WHERE a.first_name = 'PENELOPE' AND a.last_name = 'GUINESS';

queries.question: Find the most popular category by total rental count across all stores
queries.query: SELECT c.name, COUNT(r.rental_id) as total_rentals FROM category c JOIN film_category fc ON c.category_id = fc.category_id JOIN film f ON fc.film_id = f.film_id JOIN inventory i ON f.film_id = i.film_id JOIN rental r ON i.inventory_id = r.inventory_id GROUP BY c.name ORDER BY total_rentals DESC LIMIT 1;

queries.question: List films rented by customers from 'Aurora'
queries.query: SELECT DISTINCT f.title FROM film f JOIN inventory i ON f.film_id = i.film_id JOIN rental r ON i.inventory_id = r.inventory_id JOIN customer c ON r.customer_id = c.customer_id JOIN address a ON c.address_id = a.address_id JOIN city ci ON a.city_id = ci.city_id WHERE ci.city = 'Aurora' LIMIT 10;

queries.question: Find all actors who have not appeared in any 'Action' films
queries.query: SELECT a.first_name, a.last_name FROM actor a WHERE a.actor_id NOT IN (SELECT fa.actor_id FROM film_actor fa JOIN film_category fc ON fa.film_id = fc.film_id JOIN category c ON fc.category_id = c.category_id WHERE c.name = 'Action') LIMIT 10;

queries.question: Find addresses with the most customers
queries.query: SELECT a.address, COUNT(c.customer_id) as count FROM customer c JOIN address a ON c.address_id = a.address_id GROUP BY a.address ORDER BY count DESC LIMIT 5;

queries.question: List films that are in both 'Family' and 'Comedy' categories (implied via separate films logic, but maybe same film? unlikely, simplified to Films in 'Family' OR 'Comedy' with rating 'G')
queries.query: SELECT f.title FROM film f JOIN film_category fc ON f.film_id = fc.film_id JOIN category c ON fc.category_id = c.category_id WHERE c.name IN ('Family', 'Comedy') AND f.rating = 'G' LIMIT 10;

queries.question: Find the store with the most inventory items
queries.query: SELECT s.store_id, COUNT(i.inventory_id) as inventory_count FROM store s JOIN inventory i ON s.store_id = i.store_id GROUP BY s.store_id ORDER BY inventory_count DESC LIMIT 1;

queries.question: Find actors acting in films released in 2006
queries.query: SELECT DISTINCT a.first_name, a.last_name FROM actor a JOIN film_actor fa ON a.actor_id = fa.actor_id JOIN film f ON fa.film_id = f.film_id WHERE f.release_year = 2006 LIMIT 10;

queries.question: List addresses in the same city as Store 1
queries.query: SELECT a.address FROM address a JOIN city ci ON a.city_id = ci.city_id WHERE ci.city_id = (SELECT a2.city_id FROM store s JOIN address a2 ON s.address_id = a2.address_id WHERE s.store_id = 1) LIMIT 10;

queries.question: List active staff members and their store city
queries.query: SELECT s.first_name, s.last_name, ci.city FROM staff s JOIN address a ON s.address_id = a.address_id JOIN city ci ON a.city_id = ci.city_id WHERE s.active = true;

queries.question: Find films with 'Trailers' as a special feature in 'Action' category
queries.query: SELECT f.title FROM film f JOIN film_category fc ON f.film_id = fc.film_id JOIN category c ON fc.category_id = c.category_id WHERE c.name = 'Action' AND f.special_features::text LIKE '%Trailers%' LIMIT 10;

queries.question: List customers in 'London' city
queries.query: SELECT c.first_name, c.last_name FROM customer c JOIN address a ON c.address_id = a.address_id JOIN city ci ON a.city_id = ci.city_id WHERE ci.city = 'London';

queries.question: List films rated 'PG' in 'French' language
queries.query: SELECT f.title FROM film f JOIN language l ON f.language_id = l.language_id WHERE f.rating = 'PG' AND l.name = 'French' LIMIT 10;

queries.question: List rentals processed by Staff ID 1
queries.query: SELECT r.rental_id, r.rental_date FROM rental r WHERE r.staff_id = 1 LIMIT 10;

queries.question: List actors in film 'ZOOLANDER FICTION'
queries.query: SELECT a.first_name, a.last_name FROM actor a JOIN film_actor fa ON a.actor_id = fa.actor_id JOIN film f ON fa.film_id = f.film_id WHERE f.title = 'ZOOLANDER FICTION';

queries.question: List store addresses with postal codes
queries.query: SELECT s.store_id, a.address, a.postal_code FROM store s JOIN address a ON s.address_id = a.address_id;

queries.question: List films with replacement cost under 15 in 'Comedy' category
queries.query: SELECT f.title, f.replacement_cost FROM film f JOIN film_category fc ON f.film_id = fc.film_id JOIN category c ON fc.category_id = c.category_id WHERE c.name = 'Comedy' AND f.replacement_cost < 15 LIMIT 10;

queries.question: List 5 customers with the most rentals
queries.query: SELECT c.first_name, c.last_name, COUNT(r.rental_id) as total_rentals FROM customer c JOIN rental r ON c.customer_id = r.customer_id GROUP BY c.customer_id ORDER BY total_rentals DESC LIMIT 5;

queries.question: Average film length by category
queries.query: SELECT c.name, AVG(f.length) as avg_length FROM category c JOIN film_category fc ON c.category_id = fc.category_id JOIN film f ON fc.film_id = f.film_id GROUP BY c.name ORDER BY avg_length DESC;

queries.question: Total inventory items count per store
queries.query: SELECT s.store_id, COUNT(i.inventory_id) as total_items FROM store s JOIN inventory i ON s.store_id = i.store_id GROUP BY s.store_id;

queries.question: Top 5 actors by number of films
queries.query: SELECT a.first_name, a.last_name, COUNT(fa.film_id) as film_count FROM actor a JOIN film_actor fa ON a.actor_id = fa.actor_id GROUP BY a.actor_id ORDER BY film_count DESC LIMIT 5;

queries.question: List customers who have rented more than 5 times
queries.query: SELECT c.first_name, c.last_name, COUNT(r.rental_id) as rental_count FROM customer c JOIN rental r ON c.customer_id = r.customer_id GROUP BY c.customer_id HAVING COUNT(r.rental_id) > 5 ORDER BY rental_count DESC LIMIT 10;

queries.question: Categories with more than 60 films
queries.query: SELECT c.name, COUNT(fc.film_id) as film_count FROM category c JOIN film_category fc ON c.category_id = fc.category_id GROUP BY c.name HAVING COUNT(fc.film_id) > 60 ORDER BY film_count DESC;

queries.question: Top 5 staff members by number of rentals processed
queries.query: SELECT staff_id, COUNT(*) as rentals_processed FROM rental GROUP BY staff_id ORDER BY rentals_processed DESC LIMIT 5;

queries.question: Most popular film rating in each store's inventory
queries.query: SELECT s.store_id, f.rating, COUNT(i.inventory_id) as count FROM store s JOIN inventory i ON s.store_id = i.store_id JOIN film f ON i.film_id = f.film_id GROUP BY s.store_id, f.rating ORDER BY s.store_id, count DESC;

queries.question: Customers who have rented films in 'Horror' category
queries.query: SELECT DISTINCT c.first_name, c.last_name FROM customer c JOIN rental r ON c.customer_id = r.customer_id JOIN inventory i ON r.inventory_id = i.inventory_id JOIN film_category fc ON i.film_id = fc.film_id JOIN category cat ON fc.category_id = cat.category_id WHERE cat.name = 'Horror' LIMIT 10;
